Charles Bukeko (10 Julaị 1962 - 18 Julaị 2020) bụ onye Kenya na-eme ihe nkiri na onye na-eme ihe ọchị.  A maara ya maka igosi onye isi na usoro telivishọn Papa Shirandula, nke o mekwara ma merie 2010 Kalasha Award for Best Actor in a TV Series.  Bukeko pụtakwara na ihe nkiri afọ 2012 The Captain of Nakara Bukeko nwụrụ na Julaị 18, 2020 site na ihe yiri mgbaàmà COVID-19.

Bukeko bụ nwa mbụ n'ime ụmụ anọ nne na nna ya bụ Valeria Makokha na Cosmas Wafula. A mụrụ ya na Busia, Kenya.  Bukeko gara Jogoo Road Primary School wee gaa Upper Hill Secondary, ụlọ akwụkwọ Middle na Nairobi, ebe ọ nwetara Kenya Certificate of Secondary Education (KCSE).

Bukeko lụrụ Beatrice Ebbie Andega ma ha mụtara ụmụ atọ: Tony, Charlie na Wendy. Bukeko nwere ọrịa shuga.  Ọ nwụrụ n'ụlọ ọgwụ Karen dị na Nairobi, Kenya, na 18 Julaị 2020, mgbe ọ butere COVID-19 n'oge ọrịa COVID-19 na Kenya. Ọ dị afọ 58, ọ nwụrụ ụbọchị asatọ mgbe ụbọchị ọmụmụ ya gasịrị.
